Pre-Game Insights: Pakistan cricket team and Ireland cricket team will play a 3-match T20I series ahead of the T20 World Cup 2024.
Pakistan is engaged in a T20 series to prepare for the upcoming tournament.
The first match of the series will begin on May 10 at the Clontarf Cricket Club in Dublin.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Indian fans can watch Pakistan vs Ireland T20 series live streaming on Fancode app.
The Pak vs Ire T20 match will not be available on television in India.
All three matches of the Pakistan vs Ireland T20 series will be played in Dublin at the Clontarf Cricket Club.
